<div id="left">
  <h2>Rent a Clubhouse</h2>
  <small>For small and large groups</small>
  <br>
  <p>
    You have only a smaller company? Looking for something nearby?
    Than you might be well with a Clubhouse. For example from a sports club.
    Mostly there are cheap but still very good ones.
  </p>
  <br>

  <div class="row" id="location_listing">
    <% if !@locations.empty? %>
      <%= render partial: 'locations/location_list' %>
    <% else %>
      <%= render partial: 'pages/no_locations_found' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="right">
  <!-- google map -->
  <div id="map" data-mapdata='<%= raw @simple_locations.to_json.gsub("</", "<\\/") %>' class="maps-area-multiple">

  <%= javascript_include_tag('maps_location_list') %>
  </div>
</div>
